Title: Hollywood Sequel Doctor
Writer: Keegan-Michael Key (creator), Jordan Peele (creator), Rebecca Drysdale, Colton Dunn, Phil Augusta Jackson, Jay Martel, Ian Roberts, Alex Rubens, Charlie Sanders, Rich Talarico
Actors: Keegan-Michael Key, Jordan Peele, Tatyana Ali, Granville Ames
Plot: A tickle game between two friends gets weird, a writers' room brainstorms for "Gremlins 2," a man deals with an unruly office janitor, two thugs suspect their friend snitched, and Keegan and Jordan discuss Africa at a party.
